# EYEWEAR Package Diagrams (Simplified)

## Backend Package Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Backend["EYEWEAR Backend System"]
        Controllers["Controllers"]
        Services["Services"]
        Models["Models"]
        Common["Common"]
    end

    Controllers --> Services
    Services --> Models
    Controllers --> Common

    Controllers["Controllers: Auth, User, Product, Order, Return, Inventory, Payment"]
    Services["Services: Auth, User, Product, Order, Return, Inventory, VNPay"]
    Models["Models: User, Product, Order, Return, Inventory, Cart"]
    Common["Common: Guards, DTOs, Utils"]
```

---

## Frontend Package Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["EYEWEAR Frontend System"]
        Pages["Pages"]
        Components["Components"]
        Services["Services"]
        State["State"]
        Utils["Utils"]
    end

    Pages --> Components
    Pages --> Services
    Pages --> State
    Services --> Utils

    Pages["Pages: Home, Store, Product Detail, Cart, Checkout, Dashboard"]
    Components["Components: VirtualTryOn, ProductCard, CartDrawer, CheckoutForm"]
    Services["Services: authApi, productApi, cartApi, orderApi, paymentApi"]
    State["State: authStore, cartStore, productStore"]
    Utils["Utils: validators, formatters, constants"]
```

---

## Mobile Package Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Mobile["EYEWEAR Mobile System"]
        Screens["Screens"]
        Components["Components"]
        Services["Services"]
        Navigation["Navigation"]
        Utils["Utils"]
    end

    Screens --> Components
    Screens --> Services
    Screens --> Navigation
    Services --> Utils

    Screens["Screens: Login, Home, Product List, TryOn, Cart, Profile"]
    Components["Components: ProductCard, TryOnView, CameraView"]
    Services["Services: authService, productService, cartService"]
    Navigation["Navigation: TabNav, StackNav"]
    Utils["Utils: storage, validators, helpers"]
```

---

## Combined Package Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Platform["EYEWEAR Platform"]
        Frontend["Frontend\nNext.js"]
        Mobile["Mobile\nReact Native"]
        Backend["Backend\nNestJS"]
        Shared["Shared Package"]
    end

    Frontend --> Backend
    Mobile --> Backend
    Frontend --> Shared
    Mobile --> Shared
    Backend --> Shared
```

---

## Quick Summary

| Platform | Main Packages | Description |
|----------|--------------|-------------|
| **Backend** | Controllers, Services, Models, Common | NestJS REST API |
| **Frontend** | Pages, Components, Services, State | Next.js Web App |
| **Mobile** | Screens, Components, Services, Navigation | React Native App |
| **Shared** | Types, Enums, Constants | Common TypeScript types |

